  - importer `dg_public_api::feature_two::handler` belongs to feature `feature_two`
  - import `dg_public_api::feature_one::internals::secret` belongs to feature `feature_one` but is not in its public API
  - public_api patterns: `dg_public_api::feature_one::api::*`
  fix: import through `feature_one`'s public API, or expand its public_api list to include `dg_public_api::feature_one::internals::secret` if this access is intentional

